            <title><![CDATA[【🤰🏻#怀孕前一定要对乳房做全面检查#】一位27岁的孕妈在青春期时，一侧乳房里长了一颗乳腺纤维瘤，直径约2厘米。怀孕七八个月时，纤维瘤直径长到快10厘米...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【🤰🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%80%80%E5%AD%95%E5%89%8D%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E8%A6%81%E5%AF%B9%E4%B9%B3%E6%88%BF%E5%81%9A%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E6%A3%80%E6%9F%A5%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%80%80%E5%AD%95%E5%89%8D%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E8%A6%81%E5%AF%B9%E4%B9%B3%E6%88%BF%E5%81%9A%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E6%A3%80%E6%9F%A5%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#怀孕前一定要对乳房做全面检查#</span></a>】一位27岁的孕妈在青春期时，一侧乳房里长了一颗乳腺纤维瘤，直径约2厘米。怀孕七八个月时，纤维瘤直径长到快10厘米！尽管医生曾建议过她手术，考虑到妊娠安全性，她还是决定等宝宝出生后再做。结果纤维腺瘤疯长到直径20厘米，严重压迫血管，不仅乳头颜色发黑了，乳头附近区域也缺血坏死，最后只能切除一侧乳房。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[裂开]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/fc_liekai-9df295d44f.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%80%80%E5%AD%95%E5%90%8E%E4%B9%B3%E8%85%BA%E7%BB%93%E8%8A%82%E7%96%AF%E9%95%BF%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E4%B8%8D%E5%88%87%E9%99%A4%E4%B9%B3%E6%88%BF%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%80%80%E5%AD%95%E5%90%8E%E4%B9%B3%E8%85%BA%E7%BB%93%E8%8A%82%E7%96%AF%E9%95%BF%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E4%B8%8D%E5%88%87%E9%99%A4%E4%B9%B3%E6%88%BF%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#怀孕后乳腺结节疯长不得不切除乳房#</span></a> <br><br><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>小卫提醒各位备孕中的姐妹，孕前一定要做好乳房体检，一旦有不明显的炎症表现或摸到包块、出现乳头溢血等异常症状，不要犹豫，立即到正规专业医院就诊，有必要时进行肿块的活检。<br><br>最后再说一嘴，怀孕期接受乳腺超声检查，并不会影响胎儿健康，大家不用担心！<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[许愿星]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/a8/2022_WishingStar_org.png" data-rsshub-image="href" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>（慢病界）<img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hnkjj4197nj20rs0kumzy.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
            <pubDate>Sat, 09 Mar 2024 02:39:22 GMT</pubDate>
