        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[【[伤心]#为什么打了HPV疫苗还会得宫颈癌#？】北京大学第一医院妇产科主任医师毕蕙介绍：①目前的HPV疫苗，不能完全预防导致宫颈癌的所有HPV亚型；②HPV疫苗对已...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[伤心]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/l_shangxin-49b2fe44a6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E6%89%93%E4%BA%86HPV%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E8%BF%98%E4%BC%9A%E5%BE%97%E5%AE%AB%E9%A2%88%E7%99%8C%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E6%89%93%E4%BA%86HPV%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E8%BF%98%E4%BC%9A%E5%BE%97%E5%AE%AB%E9%A2%88%E7%99%8C%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#为什么打了HPV疫苗还会得宫颈癌#</span></a>？】<br>北京大学第一医院妇产科主任医师毕蕙介绍：<br>①目前的HPV疫苗，不能完全预防导致宫颈癌的所有HPV亚型；②HPV疫苗对已感染的人无治疗作用；③虽然宫颈癌与HPV的感染关系非常密切，但有非常小比例的宫颈癌与HPV不相关；④在没有接触病毒前接种疫苗（最佳年龄在9-14岁），能获得更好效果。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE25%E5%B2%81%E5%90%8E%E5%AE%9A%E6%9C%9F%E5%8F%82%E5%8A%A0%E5%AE%AB%E9%A2%88%E7%99%8C%E7%AD%9B%E6%9F%A5%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE25%E5%B2%81%E5%90%8E%E5%AE%9A%E6%9C%9F%E5%8F%82%E5%8A%A0%E5%AE%AB%E9%A2%88%E7%99%8C%E7%AD%9B%E6%9F%A5%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#医生建议25岁后定期参加宫颈癌筛查#</span></a>👇🏻（央视新闻）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:5009631395643403" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hnjhc0padaj608t0bqn1u02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/MMBo1cs0lx08d7zQ6DJ601041200oyUi0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=720x1280.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1709975652&amp;ssig=OLt2h%2Bx1xQ&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/cxauvMidlx08d7zPBCIM01041200e08o0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=540x960.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1709975652&amp;ssig=HbVCv1mbmT&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/xmH2JPxBlx08d7zPRk0o010412007Lun0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=360x640.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1709975652&amp;ssig=PjLNmm7X2Z&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A5009631395643403" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
