            <title><![CDATA[【[给你小心心]#月经是女性健康的晴雨表#】医生提醒，正常月经有4大标准，快来自查[开学季]：①月经周期：从月经第一天到下次月经来的第一天，共28天左右为一个...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[给你小心心]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/qixi2018_xiaoxinxin-c76bf85343.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%9C%88%E7%BB%8F%E6%98%AF%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A7%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E7%9A%84%E6%99%B4%E9%9B%A8%E8%A1%A8%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%9C%88%E7%BB%8F%E6%98%AF%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A7%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E7%9A%84%E6%99%B4%E9%9B%A8%E8%A1%A8%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#月经是女性健康的晴雨表#</span></a>】医生提醒，正常月经有4大标准，快来自查<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[开学季]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/72/2021_kaixueji_org.png" data-rsshub-image="href" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>：①月经周期：从月经第一天到下次月经来的第一天，共28天左右为一个周期；②经期：月经维持的时间一般在3-7天；③月经量：整个经期出血量大约在50毫升左右；④经期以外的时间出血，可能是异常阴道出血，需要及时关注。👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（CCTV生活圈）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:5009433856507976" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">CCTV生活圈的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/orj480/713e54f1ly1hniunif5zdj21hc0u075x.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/YkQEoNa5lx08d6HaYExO01041200lu180E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1709975652&amp;ssig=lm%2BobcfDgg&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/Y8r5UkIwlx08d6HacmHu01041200aVal0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1709975652&amp;ssig=X%2Fppsdg8m%2F&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/H0uNYOahlx08d6Ha3cf6010412006PdD0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1709975652&amp;ssig=SmtLfqo47V&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A5009433856507976" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
